On 4th April, day with highest average dwell times, the average dwell times were highest between 1 - 31 April, which peaked at 124 mins.
On 24th April, day with lowest average dwell times, the average dwell times were highest between 1 - 31 April, which peaked at 1 mins.
NTUC Fairprice has the highest average dwell time of 30.2 mins, with dwellers most commonly visiting from 10AM-12PM.
KFC has the lowest average dwell time of 4.2 mins, with dwellers mostly visiting from 10AM-12PM.
In May 2022, 50% of patrons were families, 20% were young couples, and delivery riders, white collared workers, and Persona 5 made up 10% of the patrons each.
